                     <interp inst="t18080113-37-off213" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18080113-37-off213" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18080113-37-cd214" type="crimeDate">13th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18080113-37-off213 t18080113-37-cd214"></join>, a pair of shoes, value 5 s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t18080113-37-victim408" type="victimName">
                        John 
                        Hale
                     <interp inst="t18080113-37-victim408" type="surname" value="Hale"></interp>
